description._content: Collection: Crowe (Milburn J.) Photograph Album Call number: PI/2005.0015 System ID: 94508. Link to the catalog The Crowe (Milburn J.) album. (top left) indexed as: J. E. Ousley notes: “J. E. Ousley.” Joseph Emory Ousley (Bolivar County Circuit Clerk and former resident of Davis Bend). (top right) indexed as: W. T. Montgomery notes: “W. T. Montgomery.” Loose photograph appears to be one of the Davis brothers, rather than a Montgomery. (bottom left) indexed as: Willis Clayton notes: “Willis Clayton.” Photographs apparently switched; this may be Carrie Hargrove. (bottom right) indexed as: Carrie Hargrove notes: “Carrie Hargrove.” Photographs apparently switched; this may be Willis Clayton. Please see our profile page for information on ordering. Credit: Courtesy of the Mississippi Department of Archives and History
